Introduction
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
SoChatty is an example of a realtime chat based on the Websocket protocol.


Usage
¯¯¯¯¯
We start the Websocket server:
    $ php Server.php

And all you have to do is to open the index.html page in many browsers with
different devices. Enjoy SoChatty!


